extendedInfo.description: Internet Booster is the application that will boost up your internet connection by 25-50% , you can boost MTU, clear DNS cache, change android files settings and speed up downloading your files.Functions: clear dns cache, boost MTU to better ping, speed up downloading, better video prebuffering for example in youtube application, clear browser cache and optimize browser settings by turn on experimental browser functions like 2D accelerating, better ping in games, faster opening websites by short time of refreshing.It will reduce your memory and CPU usage as well as allocate new video memory for your graphics device (GPU).if you have any problem regarding this app then please mail us before leaving comment. we assure you about the solution.This app might not work on some android devices, we regret for that.Permissions:internet and related permissions are needed for better user experienceDisclaimer: This Internet booster is a pure placebo. Use this application only to prank your friends. with the help of this app we can make our users believe that their internet is indeed working faster and thus make them happy.We disclaimed every questions, about advertisement and about placebo, have EULA in application. We are clear and do right with Google Policy Program and Content Rules.for internet booster, check XDA thread for more informationif you dont know about rooting your phone check http://xda-developers.com and more info about the patch (original source where i take this) http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1346680
